dialogue.introduction: I'm Kikuzuki, let's move out together
dialogue.library_intro: I'm Kikuzuki, 9th of Mutsuki-class Destroyers. In the very early part of the war, I participated in lots of capture operations. And in the latter part, I engaged in fleet-guard. It may not look so, but fleet-guard is an important mission for certain.
dialogue.secretary3: Uuu, W-what do you want, seriously?
dialogue.secretaryidle: ...That's right, I'm used to being left behind. Please don't mind me, it'll be lonely otherwise...
dialogue.wedding: If this war is over… can't I stay with you, Commander…? It can't be happening, can it…?
dialogue.equipment2: I won't say thanks... What will I use this power for...
dialogue.docking_minor_damage: Is it alright if I don't go to the front lines?
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: Uu, it's actually hurts... I don't want to sink
dialogue.ship_construction: Another ship have to throw herself into the battlefield again huh...
dialogue.start_a_sortie: Fleet, let's do our best on sortie!
dialogue.night_battle: Too bad that this place is going to be your graveyard!
dialogue.night_attack: Seems like luck isn't on your side!
dialogue.artillery_spotting: Seems like luck isn't on your side!
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: Seems like luck isn't on your side!
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: Seems like luck isn't on your side!
dialogue.mvp: This is, something not to be proud of...
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Kuh, I, Kikuzuki, am not going to sink from this!
dialogue.sunk: Let's meet at the sakura tree on that hill
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: Commander, it seems today is a special day...It's good if we could celebrate it together...
dialogue.christmas_2015: Christmas, huh? It's fine (for you) to celebrate with the people you like. W-What! Commander, are you... giving this to me?
dialogue.new_year_2016: Commander, Happy New Year. I'll be with you this year as well. There's nothing to worry about.
dialogue.setsubun_2016: It's Setsubun, huh. You should participate if you like it... Who was that!? Who threw beans at my back!? ... Mu-, Mutsuki!
